commit message:
remove hr -> sl symlinks in preparation for copying

I got bitten by these since they confused scripts, and the result was inconsistent.
Re-add the Croatian (hr) layout as a copy of the (sl) one, including 4-row layout this time.

Check-keymap scripts: add export to text format

This is part of the planned migration to non-XML editable layout definitions.

Add dead keys to French AZERTY layout:

- dead circumflex and diaeresis on the key right of 'p'
(and removed the redundant tilde there)

- dead acute and tilde as ? (top row) long-press alternates

- dead grave as ? (top row) long-press alternate
